- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possibility as the paper deals with many-to-one and many-to-many communication scenarios. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper discusses signal processing techniques for extracting signals from a subspace. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses the use of steering vectors to uniquely identify transmitters and resolve interference.
